ODFL     TITLE 'E X H I B I T  ***  132-BYTE WIDE SCREEN LAYOUT MODULE'
EXHODFLT START 0                                           ADDED 88249
*
*        EXHODFLT PROVIDES THE NEW 3180 LAYOUS FOR SUPPORTED (27*132)
*        AND LOCAL (35*132, 43*132) WIDE SCREEN DEFINITIONS.
*        EXHDZZZZ IS MANDATORY , SINCE IT CONTROLS I/O TO THE CRT.
*
*        THREE SCREEN MAPPINGS ARE REQUIRED, ONE SET FOR EACH
*        SUPPORTED LARGE SCREEN SIZE.
*
*        EXHO MODULES ARE USED BY EXHAMODS IN RESPONSE TO A MODIFY
*        (LAYOUT= ) COMMAND, AND AT INITIALIZATION TIME FROM THE
*        EXEC CARD PARM FIELD AND/OR THE &LAYOUT OPTION.
*
         EJECT ,
